### 7.3 Dashboard pages (what each page answers)

1. **Market Overview & Demographics** — city distribution, sector dominance, work-mode composition, experience demand.
2. **Financial & Salary Insights** — salary distribution, role/sector comparisons, compensation benchmarks.
3. **Entry-Level & Fresher Dynamics** — specific analysis for 0–1 years experience.
4. **Enterprise & Corporate Benchmarking** — company rankings, company-type comparisons, openings vs applicant funnel indicators.

### 7.4 Key findings (from my analysis)

- **IT leads job volume:** **35%** of listings
- **Bangalore has the highest job volume:** **28%** of listings
- **On-site dominates:** **52%** of listings
- **Unicorns pay more than MNCs:** **~15% higher** on average
- **FinTech pays highest for freshers** (as observed in the entry-level cut)

